result.name: 潮福蒸氣石鍋

reviews.text: Yes! Go if you can. Great crab and friendly service. They serve up the food so you can focus on eating not dissecting. Healthy steamed fish and veggie dishes are a treat for your eyes and stomach. My Japanese friends were delighted. Allow an extra few minutes to find this place as it can be awkward to find first time around.

The seafood is fresh, any fault in the seafood will be very obvious as they only steam the seafood. Steaming seafood is a very traditional Canton way to cook them, it retained most of the original aroma and umami of the seafood. At the end of the course, at the bottom the the port there is a congee, and all the previously steamed seafood fluids will drop into the congee, making it a naturally sweet and tasty. Magnificent!! 
By the way, the service is very good, that every table have a person to serve you, so as to ensure the best steaming time will be applied to different seafood.

You can choose meat, fish, shell fish, vegetables to steam. There is a section for making your own sauce for steamed foods, eg soy sauce, spring onions & chilli etc... The bottom of the pot contains rice which is cooked with all liquid from steam foods. You eat the rice at the very end and that was super delicious. here is all you can eat course but it seems like limited numbers per night so we couldn’t choose the option. Friendly staff but limited English. Still easy to order and the staff cook for you. I would definitely go back and would recommend. Good for taking visitors to introduce lovely HK foods.
so delicious Lobster I enjoyed ;)
seafood is fresh, taste is good, service is good, price is good, location is good., everything is good.....Thank you so much to provide us a fantastic dinner tonight.

潮福既蒸鍋我覺得唔錯…有半自助套餐已包括燉湯(不過麻麻地), 半隻乳鴿, 蜆同半隻龍蝦…再係7款海鮮選4款海鮮。之後可以任食各式丸類…蔬菜。之後仲有粥食😍😍而且還有指定啤酒氣水任飲…太約$400/人。價錢算合理…

今迄食べた香港での料理で
上位に入る店。
数種類の醤を自分の好みにカスタマイズして味わえる。
最後のお粥は最高です。
首創蒸氣火鍋 ，材料新鮮， 服務態度中上， 價錢大眾化 ，適合一家大細，二人世界，環境舒適幽靜， 值得推介，👍
